data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Do not go any further! This 4/2 really stands out and will give you the pride of ownership. This property is very well kept and you will be amazed when you get in will all the upgrades. It has tile throughout and stainless steel appliances. There is plenty of space for a big family in this desirable Silver Ridge Community. In addition, there is large backyard if you enjoy planting. This home is centrally located and is near everything. Don't wait because this one will not last.
